data.description:
Step inside this newly remodeled home adorned with new luxury vinyl flooring, creating a sophisticated ambiance complemented by neutral fresh paint tones and updated light fixtures. The heart of this home lies in its renovated kitchen, featuring granite countertops, newly installed backsplash, and shiny stainless steel appliances easily cleaned. This welcoming home invites you to experience a style of privacy in a newly renovated home with 2 auto garage, central heat/air conditioning, refrigerator, dishwasher, washer and dryer included with interior utility for easy access. A desirable location, a short distance to FM 529 to the North, 99 Parkway to the West. Located near Grocery stores, meat markets, restaurants- all types, convenience stores, pharmacies and walking distance to the neighborhood playground and gazebo. Schedule a tour now and seize the opportunity to lease this ready to move-in home. Bookmark listing...interior pics coming soon.
